{"tid":2048586,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"芝加哥公布改革警隊方案 改革警隊刻不容緩 設基金助受影響店舖","createTime":"2020-06-03T02:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T02:21:12.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"20157938974d5d14cb421221894ae3a85d9774fe","tid":2048586,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"芝加哥公布改革警隊方案<br />\n03.06.2020 10:04<br />\n<br />\n白人警員暴力執法導致美國黑人弗洛伊德死亡，激發全美多地反警暴遊行示威，並出現衝突及破壞搶掠場面。芝加哥市率先宣布改革警隊方案，邀請社區領袖及教師參與改進警員培訓，強制所有警員參與危機管理和程序公義的培訓課程。市長萊特富特表示，改革警隊刻不容緩，承認以往加強警隊問責的改革進程太慢，範圍亦過於狹窄，會爭取90天內落實新措施。另外當局會設立1000萬美元的基金，協助受示威者破壞的店舖恢復營業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1298247&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1298247%26csid%3D261_367&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgQaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=680dc702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1298247&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"dfcf412034cc756a6edc735251e422ea777c095a","tid":2048586,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:11:49.000Z","msg":"香港示威左成年都未改革<br />\n林鄭政府真係威"},{"pid":"4dae835ac7922eca0ea66f843150d166cc94dbad","tid":2048586,"uid":254383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmtX59o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmtX59o.jpg&h=be1564ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c99ce07185665ff36f49e2f02b6e4c3cb3f2397","tid":2048586,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:21:12.000Z","msg":"香港<br />\n<br />\n警魔輪姦女市民<br />\n刑事檢控專員梁卓然誓要屈到受害人坐監滅聲"}]}